# Faz 8: Notification System

## Goal

In-app bildirim + e-posta outbox pattern kurulur. 28 notification template seed. Domain event → decoupled `NotificationService` trigger (TASK_ASSIGNED, CASE_TRANSITION, SLA_WARNING, vb.). Worker `notification-dispatcher.job.ts`; içeriksiz e-posta şablonları. Cron: sla-reminder (5 dk), silent-acceptance schedule, audit-chain-verify (günlük), retention-purge (legal_hold check). NotificationBell (30 sn polling) + S-NOTIFICATION-CENTER.

Detay: `Docs/10_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md` §Faz 8.

**Bağımlılık:** Faz 5–6 (transition/task side-effects), Faz 3 (audit worker), Faz 6 `silent-acceptance.job.ts` → bu fazda cron schedule bağlanır.

