## Constraints

### Use

- Outbox fail-closed same tx as domain op
- Decoupled NotificationService enqueue
- İçeriksiz e-posta şablonları
- Worker cron (`@nestjs/schedule`) — not setInterval
- 30 sn notification polling
- legal_hold check on retention purge
- Anonim bildirimciye e-posta yok

### Avoid

- E-postada vaka/bildirimci/rapor içeriği
- Inline notification in controllers
- setInterval crons
- 5 sn polling
- Retention purge without legal_hold check
- Frontend-only mark-read (backend persistence)

